        <li>Verification or certification that the income documented is accurate or verifiable</li>
        <li>Any guarantee that generated stubs will be accepted by any specific lender, landlord, or third party</li>
      </ul>

      <p>The calculations are based on publicly available IRS withholding tables and state tax information, updated periodically. Tax laws change. There may be situations — complex filing statuses, multiple jobs, mid-year changes — where the tool's calculation differs from what a full payroll system would produce. The tool is designed for common scenarios and may not handle edge cases correctly.</p>

